<item>
            <title>[LU-11711] Labels or components on bugs?</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11711</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Would it be possible to enable labeling or component access to users such as myself? It would be very useful to be able to apply labels to various issues owned by others in the hopes of categorizing and tracking bugs associated with different major sub systems within lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We do this now with our internal repository and it provides us with a great method in determining ares which require additional focus both from engineering and testing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
